org.openadaptor.core
Interface IMessageProcessor

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractNodeRunner, Adaptor, EnrichmentProcessorNode, Node, Router
public interface IMessageProcessor

This is the fundamental interface in the openadaptor processing framework. It is implemented by components that can be assembled to cooperate in processing data. Adaptors, Nodes and Routers all implement this interface and they can be coupled together in any combination.
